### 启用 MCP 工具
POST http://localhost:9999/api/tools/mcp/manage
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "enable",
  "serverName": "datetime",
  "toolName": "get_current_time",
  "description": "获取当前时间"
}

### 禁用 MCP 工具
POST http://localhost:9999/api/tools/mcp/manage
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "disable",
  "serverName": "datetime",
  "toolName": "format_datetime"
}

### 查询 MCP 工具状态
POST http://localhost:9999/api/tools/mcp/manage
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "status",
  "serverName": "datetime",
  "toolName": "get_current_time"
}

### 切换 MCP 工具状态
POST http://localhost:9999/api/tools/mcp/manage
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "toggle",
  "serverName": "calculator",
  "toolName": "calculator"
}

### 获取指定服务的工具列表
POST http://localhost:9999/api/tools/mcp/list
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "serverName": "datetime",
  "includeUsageStats": true
}

### 获取所有服务的工具列表
POST http://localhost:9999/api/tools/mcp/list
Content-Type: application/json

{}
